introduction.name: Anant Kumawat
introduction.educationSmallDesc: B.Tech-CSE 2023, Institute of Technology and Management Gwalior, India.
introduction.aboutMeDesc: I am a 4th year student and pursuing B.Tech in Computer Science and Engineering. I am highly passionate to work as a Full Stack Web Developer. I like to do problem solving, DSA questions and learning new Technologies.

roleDesc: Learned the concepts of web development, HTML, CSS, MongoDB, Express.js, ReactJS, NodeJS and MYSQL, API.
Worked on projects like, creating clone of twitter and an e-commerce website. Used database, backend and frontend.

experience.role: Web App Development Winter Internship | Jan-Feb 2022
roleDesc: Created and maintained the profile page, database and dash boards of the users registered on the website, worked on coin system of amazon voucher with team. Used JWT token to verify user and hash passwords for password security.
Technologies used in this project are HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, NodeJS and MongoDB, express.js

Learn communication, time management and increased reach on social media platforms like, LinkedIn, Instagram, WhatsApp, etc. Representing and sharing the opportunities of the company for students to help them grow.
Learned to work in a team and got experience to work with new people of different technologies.
Created projects and task, based on ReactJS Technology. Worked on react hooks, axios, react component, etc.
Learned about the concepts of C programming such as array, pointers, functions, data types, control statement, etc.
Getting hands on experience of writing programs, problem solving, various pattern questions and finding errors.

website.ProjectNameDesc: MERN, NextJS, Bootstrap, Html, Css, Api, JS
ProjectDesc: We created a project named `Linnker` which solves the problem of finding the WhatsApp groups. It is a website which is made in NextJS technology. It consists of the features like login, signup, creating your own groups, search for your best-fit group, searching groups. It has an admin panel which is used verify the validity the WhatsApp group link, admin only allow valid WhatsApp group to show to the users. It solves the major problem of users to find there best-suited WhatsApp group.
We have used Technologies like Nextjs, Mongodb, Nodejs, Expressjs, Reactjs, Html, Css, Bootstrap, Api, Javascript.
